{
  "stem": "10818.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course there was an overt showing of Nazism.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were, they were marching, brown shirts, marching with flags, and sometimes at night with torch-- torch light parades.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was much of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, all kinds of assemblies and all kinds of sieg heil, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I felt shut out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, you know, I-- I didn't know enough to actually oppose it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was so much enthusiasm by people who were taken in by it that it was pretty difficult.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One way I felt shut out is when I was still in, in primary school, there were people who were allowed to carry the flags, and, and, and, and you know, greet other people.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you always had to heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in, in a class, a parallel class, in the same grade, the children voted for who should carry the flag.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the most popular girl won the vote.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Except that she was Jewish so was not allowed to carry the flag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We would never allowed to carry-- I mean, in retrospect, my parents would have been shocked if I carried a, a swastika.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was that kind of thing, where you know, they would-- well, they, they would-- they sent children with a message to another teacher, into another class.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you had to come in and say, heil Hitler, I'm sent by the teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was sent once and-- and did this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my parents were absolutely shocked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that was what we would told to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And because everything, every letter started with, with heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and, and everything was geared to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The whole populace had been totally indoctrinated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Sorry, bring me back to you know, how did I feel, what did I see.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
